      "rationale": "Three systematically refined meshes (2.1M, 5.8M, and 14.2M hexahedral cells) were evaluated at the 4.5 L/min, 3500 RPM operating point. GCI for the hemolysis index was 3.2% between the medium and fine meshes, satisfying the level 2 discretization error criterion. The medium mesh (5.8M cells) was selected for production runs."
